featured_reviews.review_id:
It is a spiritual abode to commemorate the martyrdom of IMAM HUSAIN who sacrificed every thing even 6 month infant to safeguard human values and to challenge and combat injustice and oppression of Yazid the cruel ruler of seven century Syria, Iraq . Mourning congregations are held during month of Muharram.
Here we learn through spiritual addresses by enlightened religious scholars that it is character and human values that matter significantly to make life worth while. We are entrusted with the task of making our society better and more beautiful when we follow the principle of co existence and pray to Allah only. We also salute to our twelve Imams ( Ahlebait ) who lived and died for Allah SWT and His creatures.
